---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const jsonLd = [
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "name": "Privacy Policy",
    "url": "https://theeduassist.com/privacy-policy/",
    "description": "Read how TheEduAssist collects, uses, stores, and protects information submitted through our website, review forms, email, and project inquiry flows."
  }
];
---
<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | TheEduAssist"
  description="Read how TheEduAssist collects, uses, stores, and protects information submitted through our website, review forms, email, and project inquiry flows."
  canonicalPath="/privacy-policy/"
  type="website"
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
>

  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-100 px-4 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-600">Last updated: 2026</p>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 prose prose-slate">

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>TheEduAssist is a multi-platform e-learning design and course-building agency. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect and use information when visitors use our website, submit a review request, contact us by email, or interact with our website tools.</p>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">2. Information we collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect the following information:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>name</li>
        <li>email address</li>
        <li>company/brand name</li>
        <li>project details submitted through the 24–48 Hour Review form</li>
        <li>current platform or project type</li>
        <li>budget range</li>
        <li>timeline</li>
        <li>messages sent by email</li>
        <li>basic website usage data if analytics are used</li>
        <li>technical information such as browser/device information if collected by analytics or hosting tools</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">3. How we collect information</h2>
      <p>We collect information through:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Google Form embedded on <a href="/book-free-audit/" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">/book-free-audit/</a></li>
        <li>email links using <a href="mailto:Info@theeduassist.com" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">Info@theeduassist.com</a></li>
        <li>the Tawk.to live chat widget, including chat messages, name/email if submitted, and chat metadata (such as page URL, selected package/service, and technical data) provided by the third-party chat provider.</li>
        <li>project request/message widget</li>
        <li>contact page</li>
        <li>analytics tools if enabled</li>
        <li>hosting/security tools</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-sm font-semibold p-4 bg-brand-softBg rounded-md border border-brand-border">
        <strong>Important Live Chat Notice:</strong> When using our Tawk.to live chat widget, please do not submit passwords, bank details, payment card details, government IDs, or highly confidential files in the chat.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">4. How we use information</h2>
      <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>respond to inquiries</li>
        <li>review project details</li>
        <li>recommend the right service path</li>
        <li>prepare scope, quote, or next step</li>
        <li>improve website content and services</li>
        <li>maintain website security</li>
        <li>manage client communication</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">5. Google Form notice</h2>
      <p>The 24–48 Hour Review form is powered by Google Forms. When you submit the form, your information may be processed by Google according to Google’s own terms and privacy practices.</p>
      <p><strong>Instruction:</strong> Do not submit passwords, payment details, bank details, government IDs, health records, or highly confidential files through the form.</p>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">6. Email communication</h2>
      <p>If users email TheEduAssist, their email address and message content will be used to respond to their request.</p>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">7. Analytics and cookies</h2>
      <p>TheEduAssist may use analytics or similar tools to understand website traffic and improve user experience. If analytics are enabled, these tools may collect usage information such as pages visited, device/browser details, and approximate location.</p>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">8. AI/share tools</h2>
      <p>The website may include buttons that help visitors copy a page-aware prompt and open third-party AI assistants such as ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot, or Grok. TheEduAssist does not control those third-party AI tools. If users paste content into an AI assistant, that interaction is subject to the selected AI provider’s terms and privacy policy.</p>
      <p>The site may include share buttons for LinkedIn, Facebook, X, and copy link.</p>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">9. Data sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell personal information.</p>
      <p>We may share information only with service providers needed to operate the website and respond to inquiries, such as Google Forms/Sheets, email providers, hosting providers, analytics providers, and project communication tools.</p>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">10. Data retention</h2>
      <p>We keep inquiry information only as long as needed for communication, project evaluation, business records, or legal/security purposes.</p>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">11. User rights</h2>
      <p>Users may request access, correction, or deletion of their submitted information by emailing <a href="mailto:Info@theeduassist.com" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">Info@theeduassist.com</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">12. International users</h2>
      <p>TheEduAssist may receive inquiries from different countries. By submitting information, users understand that their information may be processed through tools and services that operate internationally.</p>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">13. Security</h2>
      <p>We use reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect submitted information, but no internet transmission or storage system can be guaranteed 100% secure.</p>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">14. Children’s privacy</h2>
      <p>The website is intended for business and professional inquiries, not for children.</p>

      <h2 class="text-brand-navy">15. Contact</h2>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:Info@theeduassist.com" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">Info@theeduassist.com</a></p>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
